arChildNodes.szComment: The player returns, showing Gerti the remains of Raekor's Great Axe--destroyed by the Triune. She is disgusted that it lasted so long with her kin, only to be destroyed by fools.
Gerti analyzes the broken Great Axe, noting that it is no longer fit for battle/use.
Gerti says Raekor's Great Axe must be repairs. It cannot be left in this state, dishonoring her.
Gerti describes materials she requires to repair Raekor's Great Axe: A demon's horn, hardend by hire.
Gerti describes materials she requires to repair Raekor's Great Axe: Silver Quartz, a rare ore.
Gerti requests the player bring the materials to her so that she may repair Raekor's Great Axe--proving to the Triune that it is not so easily destroyed.
